T1  - Order book characteristics and the volume–volatility relation: Empirical evidence from a limit order market
AU  - Næs, Randi
AU  - Skjeltorp, Johannes A.
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 9
IS  - 4
SP  - 408
EP  - 432
PY  - 2006
